  "prompt": "Which are the least expensive and still good 3D/4D cinema theaters in Delhi NCR?",
  "response": "Delhi NCP offers a range of cinemas where you can enjoy 3D/4D movies at reasonable prices. Below are some of the least expensive yet good-quality options for 3D/4D cinema experiences in Delhi NCR:\n\n### 1. **PVR Cinemas (Select Low-Cost Locations)**\n   - **Example:** PVR ECX (Priya Cinema, Basant Lok) or PVR M2K (Rohini)\n   - **Why:** PVR is known for its quality, but some locations offer tickets at lower prices, especially during weekday matinees or with offers on apps like BookMyShow or PayTM.\n\n### 2. **INOX Cinemas**\n   - **Example:** INOX Nehru Place, INOX Naraina\n   - **Why:** INOX offers competitive pricing and good-quality 3D/4D experiences. Look for discounted tickets during weekdays or early shows.\n\n### 3. **Cinepolis**\n   - **Example:** Cinepolis Fun Cinemas (Janak Place)\n   - **Why:** Cinepolis often runs promotions and offers affordable tickets for 3D movies, especially in suburban areas.\n\n### 4. **Wave Cinemas**\n   - **Example:** Wave Cinemas (Kirti Nagar, Noida)\n   - **Why:** Wave Cinemas are budget-friendly and provide a decent 3D experience. They frequently offer discounts through their app or loyalty programs.\n\n### 5. **Movie Time Cinemas**\n   - **Example:** Movie Time Cinemas (Pitampura)\n   - **Why:** Known for being one of the most affordable chains in Delhi, Movie Time Cinemas offers a good 3D experience at a low cost.\n\n### 6. **Delite Cinema**\n   - **Location:** Asaf Ali Road, Old Delhi\n   - **Why:** One of Delhi\u2019s oldest single-screen theaters, Delite offers affordable 3D movie tickets and a nostalgic experience.\n\n### 7. **M2K Cinemas**\n   - **Location:** Rohini\n   - **Why:** M2K is a budget-friendly option with decent 3D screens and affordable ticket prices.\n\n### Tips to Save Money:\n- **Weekday Shows:** Tickets are often cheaper on weekdays compared to weekends.\n- **Morning Shows:** Early shows are usually more affordable.\n- **Discount Apps:** Use apps like BookMyShow, PayTM, or M-Ticket for discounts and cashback offers.\n- **Loyalty Programs:** Join loyalty programs of cinema chains for additional discounts.\n\nThese options combine affordability with a good 3D/4D movie experience. Always check for the latest offers and discounts before booking!",
